{"tid":2070203,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 半小時晚餐 ： 雪菜火鴨絲燜米","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:38:54.000Z","uid":30742,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"282765f5f1f66c3d4044ba92621a76f55b189d06","tid":2070203,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hLBPn_ZP5F4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhLBPn_ZP5F4&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=e3aab5d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hLBPn_ZP5F4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHgdzvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHgdzvq.jpg&h=fc6302d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個足足拍左三次既火鴨絲燜米 <br />\n其實一d都唔難，<br />\n只係拍親都漏咁d鏡 <br />\n結果某人食左三次 <br />\n佢話短期內都唔好再煮喇！ <br />\n但我覺得呢個幾好呀！<br />\n又快又好食 <br />\n唔計浸雪菜，基本上半個鐘就攪掂！ <br />\n煮多餅米粉帶埋飯都得！ <br />\n<br />\n文字食譜recipe: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/06/working-day-dinner-braised-rice.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F06%2Fworking-day-dinner-braised-rice.html%20&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=a3189e6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/06/working-day-dinner-braised-rice.html </a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=ca5c7566\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=499b8f11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.